name: histidine kinase
reaction: ATP + protein L-histidine = ADP + protein N-phospho-L-histidine
comment: This entry has been included to accommodate those protein-histidine kinases for which the phosphorylation site has not been established (i.e. either the pros- or tele-nitrogen of histidine). A number of histones can act as acceptor.
